data.description: Immaculate 4-bedroom & 2.5 bath home located in the White Hall community. This gorgeous two-story home is practically new, built in 2016. You enter a spacious foyer leading into a formal dining room with a seamless transition into the kitchen and great room. The eat-in kitchen is a chef’s dream, including granite countertops, ample cabinets/counterspace, subway tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances and a large walk-in pantry! The open concept living with deck extending off the rear and fenced in backyard, makes it perfect for entertaining and enjoying morning coffee or evening wine. The primary bedroom features a tray ceiling with a large ensuite bath & large walk-in closet. White Hall offers great amenities including a pool, basketball court, tennis courts, playground, jogging path and more. Easy to show but must have confirmed appointment.
